defaultMessage: You must have at least Report Text or Visual Card selected in order to publish the report.

The report for {language} cannot be empty because it is the default language. You must have content in Report Text or Visual Card for {language}. Or, you can right-click on the tab for another language to make it the default language.
You must provide text in the content or title of Report Text, or unselect it and select Visual Card in order to publish the item.
Your item still has the default status {status} and must be changed to a different status before it can be published.
